summary: Small Simple Farm Building. Don't expect much, this is my first custom mesh.
descriptionHtml:
I wanted to see if I could make a custom mesh with 3ds Max using the farmhouse tile set meshes and textures as a base. I succeeded, somehow, even with added functional collision. It's ugly and poorly optimized (way too many seperate nitrishape nodes, but hey, at least it is something xD

Contains no LODs.

-Skyrim HD textures (compatible) and Seasons of Skyrim ENB in screenshots
author: Edje Noh
